(36461, 81492, 3491, 1, 'Sunflower', '詞/曲/演唱 by Luet\r\n\r\n', '2011-06-25 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 2, 6, 'Youʼre circling around \r\nto find a shiny sunflower\r\nto taste her sweetness\r\nas you dive in lower\r\nYouʼre like a busy bumble bee\r\nlooking for the pollens\r\ncanʼt stop\r\nfantasizing of her\r\nGive her your T L C \r\nDonʼt you flee, a loving seed\r\nʻcause thatʼs your only chance\r\nto make her feel\r\n\r\n\r\nnow just love her\r\ngo ahead you love her\r\nwith your gentleness\r\nlove her say yes youʼll love her\r\nwith your foolishness\r\nThere is nothing like your tender loving care\r\nnothing like your tender loving care\r\nonce you love her\r\n\r\nSheʼs driving you crazy\r\nnow you found that sunflower\r\nyouʼre humming upside down\r\nto make your first encounter\r\nBut she has many bumble bees\r\nfalling under her powder\r\nwhy stop\r\nbe fascinated by her\r\n\r\n(Give her your T L C\r\nDonʼt you flee, a loving seed\r\nʻcause thatʼs your only chance\r\nto make her feel\r\n\r\nnow just love her\r\ngo ahead you love her\r\nwith your gentleness\r\nlove her say yes youʼll love her\r\nwith your foolishness\r\nThere is nothing like your tender loving care\r\nnothing like your tender loving care\r\nonce you love her)\r\n\r\nsunflower\r\nsoon you''ll have her\r\nsunflower \r\n\r\n你繞著圈圈\r\n尋覓一朵閃亮的 太陽花\r\n想感受她的甜美\r\n你逐漸接近\r\n像一隻忙碌的大黃蜂\r\n探訪著花粉\r\n無法停止想念她\r\n\r\n給她你的溫柔款待\r\n愛的種子別亂紛飛\r\n因為這是你唯一打動她的機會\r\n\r\n現在就愛她\r\n用你的溫柔盡情愛她\r\n好好愛她\r\n說你會盲目地愛著她\r\n沒有什麼比得過你的溫柔對待\r\n你的溫柔對待\r\n一旦你深深愛上她\r\n\r\n她讓你神經緊繃\r\n現在你找到了那朵完美的 太陽花\r\n你嗡嗡地左顧右盼\r\n試著展開你們的第一次接觸\r\n但她身邊有好多大黃蜂\r\n拜在她的甜蜜花粉中\r\n叫人怎不為她深深著迷？\r\n\r\n給她你的溫柔款待\r\n愛的種子別亂紛飛\r\n因為這是你唯一打動她的機會\r\n\r\n所以就愛她\r\n用盡你最大的溫柔\r\n好好愛她\r\n說你會盲目地愛著她\r\n\r\n沒有什麼比得過你的溫柔對待\r\n你的溫柔對待\r\n一旦你深深愛上她\r\n太陽花 \r\n很快你將擁有她\r\n太陽花\r\n', '', 278, '', 'Luet', 'Luet', '崔', '', '', 0, 0, 0, '2011-06-21 10:35:47', '2015-03-12 13:47:35', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
